Class ConcreteAspectGeneration

  • java.lang.Object
    • intertrust.modules.ag.ConcreteAspectGeneration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenerationOfNewAspectRequestInt, GenericAspectsAdaptationRequestInt
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AspectGeneration_AspectJ

    public abstract class ConcreteAspectGeneration
extends java.lang.Object
implements GenericAspectsAdaptationRequestInt, GenerationOfNewAspectRequestInt
    Concrete Aspect Generation module. Basic functionality of the aspect generation module for a specific dependent AOP framework. This module completes the generic security adaptation plan generated by the generic aspect generation sub-module with information specific of the AOP framework used for a particular instantiation of the INTER-TRUST framework. Its input is the generic security adaptation plan (GenericAspectsAdaptationRequestInt interface), and its output is a concrete security adaptation plan (Concrete AspectsAdaptationRequestInt interface). //It is composed by two internal components: Concrete Security Adaptation Plan Generation and Concrete Aspect Generation.
    Author:
    UMA
